{"id": "1386965997352915005", "channel_id": "1386965997352915005", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "⭐**版本活動時間：**6 月 30 日 9:00 - 7 月 14 日 9:00\n\n⭐**「偉大的征服」介紹：**\n✦ 「偉大的征服」共包含 5 個挑戰關卡，活動首日開放 1 個，之後每 2 天開放 1 個。\n✦ 守密人可用活動中獲取的「美味雷歐烤肉」在「敬獻貢禮」活動商店兌換流明之芯、無垢之芯、賢石碎屑等豐富獎勵。\n\n⭐**異夢視界「征廚房記」介紹：**\n✦ 版本期間將限時免費開放。活動共設有2個劇情關卡，全部通關後，即可解鎖全新鑰令「獵食決心」。\n✦ 「獵食決心」鑰令效果：從出戰喚醒體的「技能卡」中發現 3 張，選擇 1 張將其臨時複製置入手中並使其算力消耗降低 1。若當前界域為血肉，可以選擇「一掃而光！」：將全部卡牌的臨時複製置入手中，但不再降低算力消耗。\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\n⭐**Event Duration: **June 30, 9:00 AM - July 14, 9:00 AM\n\n⭐**New Event \"The Great Conquering\":**\n✦ \"The Great Conquering\" includes a total of 5 challenge stages. One stage will be available on the first day of the event, and an additional stage will open every two days thereafter.\n✦ Exchange \"Leonian Barbecue\" obtained in the event for various rewards: Luminous Core, Pure Core, Aetheric Shard, and more at the \"Offer Tribute\" event store.\n\n⭐**New Dreamscape \"Culinary Dominion\":**\n✦ Free unlock during Version 2.2.3. The event includes 2 story stages, and upon completing all of them, you will unlock the new Posse \"Voracious Resolve\".\n✦ New Possee \"Voracious Resolve\": Discover 3 cards from the \"Skill Cards\" of all the Awakeners in your team. Choose 1 to add a Temporary Copy with -1 Arithmetica Cost into your hand. If the current Realm is Caro, you may activate \"Gobble Up!\": Put Temporary Copies of all 3 cards into your hand, but no longer reduce their Arithmetica Costs.", "timestamp": "2025-06-24T07:07:42.351000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-06-24T07:18:12.395000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "hug", "emoji_id": "1356083899553288382", "count": 13}, {"emoji": "evil", "emoji_id": "1356083443020337152", "count": 10}], "attachments": [{"id": "1386965998120468601", "filename": "3.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 4006181, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1386965997352915005/1386965998120468601/3.png?ex=69ccc43e&is=69cb72be&hm=67dc61dc452e947f48bcda32b1d2dcd16af29cc5e03df69ec6885a03efac83b3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1386965997352915005", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.3預告: 版本活動「偉大的征服」┊V2.2.3 Preview: Version Event—The Great Conquering", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
